{"id":430,"date":"2020-02-29T22:30:15","date_gmt":"2020-02-29T22:30:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/alltheplacesivecried\/"},"modified":"2023-03-22T22:33:39","modified_gmt":"2023-03-22T22:33:39","slug":"alltheplacesivecried","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/alltheplacesivecried\/","title":{"rendered":"All The Places That I&#8217;ve Cried | How Travel Made Me Soft"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">You\u2019ve probably never seen a photo of someone crying at a stunning beach on the gram. One, I\u2019m pretty sure we\u2019re all ugly criers. Two, who even thinks to take their camera out in those moments? BUT the tears do flow, sometimes just as much as the drinks do on vacay &#8211; especially if you travel full &amp; Sometimes you\u2019re crying tears of joy and other times it\u2019s loss or sadness or heartbreak. Life is nuanced &amp; if travel has taught me anything, it\u2019s that joy and sadness can exist at the same time.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>Here are some of the places I\u2019ve cried: \u2063\u2063<\/strong><br \/>\n\u2063\u2063<br \/>\nA Parisian bedroom after saying goodbye to a special adventure and an even more special someone. \u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583013752258-33IYP5Q7VKROU5CQ959W\/alltheplacesivecried\" alt=\"alltheplacesivecried\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583013752258-33IYP5Q7VKROU5CQ959W\/alltheplacesivecried\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3333\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5adf6d6b59fb4dacf0a42a\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">\u2063\u2063At a club in Colombia mere hours after being robbed. But these were tears of pure gratitude not sadness. Funny how that works. \u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2026px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Screenshot2020-02-29at35202PM.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2020-02-29 at 3.52.02 PM.png\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Screenshot2020-02-29at35202PM.png\" data-image-dimensions=\"2026x1400\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5ae571d48f8f22c9d73e29\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">Flights. Oh, countless flights. Shoutout to that flight attendant who gracefully passed me a mini-bottle of wine lmao. You\u2019re the real MVP. Something MUST be in the air on flights. \u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583013882832-T38WK7ZG4T63W4LC2T2S\/alltheplacesivecried\" alt=\"alltheplacesivecried\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583013882832-T38WK7ZG4T63W4LC2T2S\/alltheplacesivecried\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3333\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5adff47a7f3216d6b9e301\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">On a safari jeep in Kenya. So many animals. So many emotions. \u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014014157-QCDAQ19IKF64W99IW6UG\/alltheplacesivecried\" alt=\"alltheplacesivecried\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014014157-QCDAQ19IKF64W99IW6UG\/alltheplacesivecried\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x2500\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5ae0717a7f3216d6b9f76f\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">\u2063On a hidden rooftop in Greece with a bottle of wine in hand and in the arms of someone who reassured me that TEARS ARE GOOD. It must have been a perfect combination of the sunset and the person and the moment and ugh.\u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014111123-EKLR6717JUJ69WCA8BBI\/alltheplacesivecried\" alt=\"alltheplacesivecried\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014111123-EKLR6717JUJ69WCA8BBI\/alltheplacesivecried\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x1875\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5ae0d7e0cc0e63b16f8b73\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">In the arms of a new friend in a hotel in Ecuador after losing an old friend.<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014048098-S3XUIZZSGOPJ1F9F69AL\/alltheplacesivecried\" alt=\"alltheplacesivecried\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014048098-S3XUIZZSGOPJ1F9F69AL\/alltheplacesivecried\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3334\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5ae096d48f8f22c9d66998\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">\u2063 At a bar in Cuba with a stranger I had just met in a tour earlier that day discussing childhood sh*t???(she\u2019s probably reading this&#8230;hey girl ) shoutout to solo travel and the magnetic instant connections that it breeds!! \u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/IMG_0063-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0063.JPG\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/IMG_0063-scaled.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3333\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5ae528118337590d92f231\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">\u2063\u2063Feeling like I was on my deathbed after a severe case of food poisoning in Uzbekistan. \u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2316px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014649050-GJ9J64VJ43D1CO7R2H8N\/alltheplacesivecried\" alt=\"alltheplacesivecried\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014649050-GJ9J64VJ43D1CO7R2H8N\/alltheplacesivecried\" data-image-dimensions=\"2316x3088\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5ae2f6483fcf2033375d0e\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">\u2063\u2063<br \/>\nAdmiring the sheer beauty of the landscapes in Iceland from a campervan with my bestfriend \u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 1242px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/travellovelanguages.jpeg\" alt=\"travellovelanguages.jpeg\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/travellovelanguages.jpeg\" data-image-dimensions=\"1242x1239\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5ae3670054c853617031ef\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">\u2063On a night bus in Peru. Iono if it was bc I was watching La La Land or because we were literally about to fall off the side of this cliff. Emotions were running high though! \u2063\u2063<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2448px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014886889-E4Y8HNX4R9GK0U3680JO\/alltheplacesivecried\" alt=\"alltheplacesivecried\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1583014886889-E4Y8HNX4R9GK0U3680JO\/alltheplacesivecried\" data-image-dimensions=\"2448x3264\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5e5ae3e2d344ff762e2f4b71\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<p style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">\u2063\u2063<br \/>\nWhat can I say? Travel has made me soft. With such a whirlwind of experiences, the tears had to flow. I\u2019m just glad I\u2019ve learned to make space for them. Inspired by&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/haleydrewthis\/\">@haleydrewthis<\/a>&nbsp;\u2063Ever cried tears of sadness or joy on a trip?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p class=\"\">Life is nuanced &amp; if travel has taught me anything, it\u2019s that joy and sadness can exist at the same time.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":431,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"_uf_show_specific_survey":0,"_uf_disable_surveys":false,"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[306,3,10],"tags":[97,28,6,155,206],"class_list":["post-430","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-international","category-life","category-travel","tag-inspiration","tag-personal-stories","tag-travel","tag-travel-goals","tag-travel-story"],"aioseo_notic